query:
SELECT 
  i.id as locationId,
  wl.code as locationCode,
  wl.type as locationType,
  wz.name as zoneName,
  wz.code as zoneCode,
  SUM(i.quantity) as totalQuantity,
  SUM(i.reservedQuantity) as totalReserved,
  SUM(i.quantity - i.reservedQuantity) as totalAvailable,
  COUNT(DISTINCT i.productId) as productCount,
  COUNT(DISTINCT i.tenantId) as tenantCount
FROM inventory i
LEFT JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
LEFT JOIN warehouseZones wz ON wl.zoneId = wz.id
WHERE i.quantity > 0
GROUP BY i.locationId, wl.code, wl.type, wz.name, wz.code
LIMIT 5;
